      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Tom King</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:182px;\"><a href=\"https://uk.linkedin.com/in/kingtom\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/3/38/TomKing.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"237\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:TomKing.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Tom King <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Tom King</b>,<br />\na British computer scientist in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_security_management\">information security management</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and computer games programmer <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \nTom is author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> compatible <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> chess engine <a href=\"/Francesca\" title=\"Francesca\">Francesca</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1997_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1997 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>Shredder wins the 17th World Microcomputer Chess Championship</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#23_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 23, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Shredder\" title=\"Shredder\">Shredder</a>, <a href=\"/WMCCC_2000\" title=\"WMCCC 2000\">WMCCC 2000</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1997_...\">1997 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1997 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/JJTEBafyuYM/hRTys0ZxcUIJ\">Null move depth reductions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, February 02, 1997&#160;» <a href=\"/Depth_Reduction_R\" title=\"Depth Reduction R\">R</a>, <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/597f1170cfdbe640#\">32bits - enough for hashing board?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, January 13, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Zobrist_Hashing\" title=\"Zobrist Hashing\">Zobrist Hashing</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/0e56bda426a70a22#\">Null move around (beta-1, beta)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, March 05, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/462b49226d1f1dfe#\">Asymetric king safety</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, March 13, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Asymmetric_Evaluation\" title=\"Asymmetric Evaluation\">Asymmetric Evaluation</a>, <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=63511\">SEE for forward pruning in Q. Search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 04, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">SEE</a>, <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=64357\">SEE for forward pruning in the Q. search - I'm confused!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 11, 1999</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=81949\">Test suites - can they reliably predict ELO?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 11, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Test-Positions\" title=\"Test-Positions\">Test-Positions</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=126878\">Fail highs..which subsequently fail low</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 27, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">Fail-High</a>, <a href=\"/Fail-Low\" title=\"Fail-Low\">Fail-Low</a>, <a href=\"/Search_Instability\" title=\"Search Instability\">Search Instability</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=168497\">Move ordering at root of search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 07, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=183089\">Null move R=2 vs Null move R=2/3</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 09, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Depth_Reduction_R\" title=\"Depth Reduction R\">R</a>, <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=275347\">Value of playing different versions of a program against each other</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 06, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=4435&amp;p=23839\">history pruning/ late move pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 02, 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=491623\">Francesca MAD v0.11 Released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 06, 2006</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=4480&amp;p=23303\">Verified null-move pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 09, 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning#ZugzwangVerification\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Verified Null-Move Pruning</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34909\">static null move pruning in stockfish</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 13, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=35955\">move count based pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 02, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36104\">Most important eval elements</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 17, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=37514\">Using SEE to prune in main search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 08, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">SEE</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39102\">value of king tropism in eval function</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 17, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69426\">After an 8 year break..</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 30, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69481\">Simplest way to implement quick and dirty lazy smp</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 04, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69722\">Null move pruning, only when score &gt;= beta?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 25, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70217\">Depth reduced but ELO increased</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 16, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Countermove_Heuristic\" title=\"Countermove Heuristic\">Countermove Heuristic</a>, <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">Playing Strength</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=72673\">ELO value of TTSE?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 29, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Singular_Extensions#RestrictedSE\" title=\"Singular Extensions\">TTSE</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tom_King&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73012\">Endgame woes</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 07, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Draw_Evaluation\" title=\"Draw Evaluation\">Draw Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73250\">Searching fail highs shallower..</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tom King</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 02, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">Fail-High</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/in